### no_drag()
``` lua
local drag_amount = no_drag()
```

_This function is intended as a helper function for **`set_hit_props()`**._<br>
_It is functionally equivalent to `drag( Direction.None, 0 )`._

Returns a <%= @link_drag %> object with a pre-set value, that when used, will cause an attack to **not** move any <%= @link_entity %> hit.

